name: CLOWN BABY NO.4
description: This CLOWN BABY is the only one with a name - SPADE."CLOWN BABIES" is a series of character illustrations I did back in 2020. It is a collection of 7 characters inspired by emotions such as fear, sadness, shyness..., and CLOWNS. This one is the FOURTH in the series! Everyone who collects will get a ready-to-print sticker sheet file!
